quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,46,"(Tachisalilidwa kuti) gajinjilani mwantendele n’di ŵagosedwa."
  15,47,"Ni tuchityosya iwundo (ya uchimwa ni litima) yayaliji m’mitima mwao, tachiŵa (ŵakunonyelana) mwaulongo ali (atemi) pa itengu yauchimbichimbi mwakulolegana."
  15,48,"Ngagaja kwakwaya mwalakwemo masausyo galigose, soni ŵanganyao ngaaja koposyedwamo."
  16,25,"Kuti akatwichile misigo jao (jasambi) jakwanila lisiku lya Kiyama, kwisa soni misigo (jasambi) ja aŵala ŵaakwasokonesya mwangali umanyilisi (wa akusokonesedwao). Naalole, kaje kusakala misigo jachakatwichilejejo!"
  16,26,"Chisimu ŵaatesile malindi aŵala ŵaŵaliji paujo pao (ŵanya Anamuruda), nambo Allah ŵagumulile chakutaŵa chao kutandila pachitepo, basi nsakasa ni wagwilile pachanya pao, soni ilagasyo ni yaichilile kuumila upande wanganaumanyilila."
  16,27,"Kaneko lisiku lya Kiyama (Allah) tachajigasya nchesela ni tachiti: “Ali kwapi akumwanganya nao, aŵala ŵamwaliji nkukangana (ni Achimitume) yakwamba ŵanganyao?” Aŵala ŵaŵapedwile umanyilisi tachiti: “Chisimu kwaluka lelo ni ulanda ili pa achimakafili.”"